3. Ranking Engine

MVP:

Simple win/loss scoring

Better:

Elo-style system

rating[A] += K * (result - expected)
rating[B] += K * ((1-result) - expected)

Advanced:
	•	Bayesian ranking (confidence intervals)
	•	uncertainty weighting
	•	recency weighting

